These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  chef, paramedic, lawyer, bartender, manager, dressmaker, project-manager
1. the paramedic is in the middle##1
2. the paramedic is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the manager is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the chef is on the right of the lawyer##1
5. the project-manager is on the far left##1
6. the dressmaker is on the right of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Job   | project-manager | bartender | manager | paramedic | lawyer | chef | dressmaker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, weightlifting, swimming, handball, volleyball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Sport   | basketball | handball | weightlifting | volleyball | swimming | biathlon | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, surfing, skiing, baseball, golf, weightlifting, ice-hockey
