2. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Sport   | golf | cricket | weightlifting | skiing | ice-hockey | surfing | baseball |

