.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-4::.
7 different pets are kept: snake, horse, guinea-pig, rat, pony, mouse, bird
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7    |
| Pet   | bird | rat | snake | horse | guinea-pig | pony | mouse |

