.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, subway, snowmobile, quad-bike, airplane, train, bike
1. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Transport   | bike | snowmobile | quad-bike | train | roller | subway | airplane |

